Package com.ubicua.didas.resources

Class DidasRoleAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.keycloak.models.jpa.RoleAdapter
com.ubicua.didas.resources.DidasRoleAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.keycloak.models.jpa.JpaModel<org.keycloak.models.jpa.entities.RoleEntity>, org.keycloak.models.RoleModel, org.keycloak.models.RoleProviderFactory, org.keycloak.provider.ProviderFactory
public class DidasRoleAdapter extends org.keycloak.models.jpa.RoleAdapter implements org.keycloak.models.RoleProviderFactory
Adapter class that wraps a JPA RoleEntity to the Keycloak RoleModel interface, augmenting it to persist and interpret DID discovery attributes.

Overrides attribute and description handling to insert DID id, context, and service metadata per configuration.

Author:
Ivan Kuchumov
